1. Button 'Raduis':
     - step 100m
     - range 100...100_000


2. Colors od settings icons in flat panel:
    - black: default
    - white: selected & highlighted
    - red: disable


3. Reachability:
    - work only on real device (iPhone)
    - reacts to on/off connection state
    - show alert view


4. Action buttons on flat panel:
    - delete (hede panel) all stored properties
    - cancel (hide panel) without modify stored properties
    - ready (hide panel) with modify stored properties

4.1. Radius button:
      - open UIPickerView with numbers range 100...100_000
      - auto select stored radius value

4.2. Wi-Fi button:
      - open UIPickerView with current Wi-Fi network name
      - auto select stored radius value
      - work only on real device (iPhone)

4.3. Geofence button:
      - enter manual geofence
      - check empty value
      - Cancel & Ok actions


5. Flat view:
    - before show check network connection
    - enable/disable settings buttons


6. Location Manager:
